quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  52,15,"E ko mbilewu nii? Kaa hara on ngla yi'ide?"
  52,16,"Cumee e magge! Muññiɗon ma on muññaaki, fof no fota e mon. Nganndee ko njoɓeteɗon, ko ko ngollaynoɗon"."
  52,17,"Pellet, gooŋɗuɓe ɓeen hino e Aljannaaji e neemaaji,"
  52,18,"ko ɓe dakimitotooɓe ko Joomi maɓɓe okki ɓe, Joomi maɓɓe daɗndi ɓe lepte Jahiimi ɗeen."
  52,19,"[Ɓe mbi'anee] : "Ñaamee njaron, ko newi moɗdeum, sabu koko ngollaynoɗon."
  52,20,"hara ko on soɓɓindiiɓe e hoore danɗe weertindiraaɗe", Min ndesina ɓe kadi yooɗa e yaaJa gite en"
  52,21,"Ɓeen gooŋɗinɓe, geñngol maɓɓe ngol kadi jokki ɓe e gooŋɗinal, Min tawtindinay ɓe e geñngol maɓɓe ngol. Min istantaa ɓe hu'unde e golle maɓɓe ɗeen; neɗɗo kala ko faggitii kon no tiginaa."
  52,22,"Min ɓeydani ɓe muuyanteeɗi e tebbeeli kala ko ɓe tuuyetee."
  52,23,"Heɓe njaɓondira toon, ñedduɗe ɗe jillaa mehre wonaa ko bakkondinta."
  52,24,"Sukaaɓe no eeltanaaɓe hino wanngoo hakkunde maɓɓe, wa'aɓe wa kaŋŋe maraaɗe."
  52,25,"Yoga maɓɓe feewtita yoga, ɓe laɓndondira;"
  52,26,"ɓe mbi'a: "Pellet, min laatino ado [hannde], hulnooɓe [lepte ɗeen] hakkunde yimɓe amen";"
  52,27,"Allah moƴƴii e amen, O daɗni meon lepte Norngal."
  52,28,"Min laatino ado [hannde], torotonooɓe Mo. Pellet, ko Kaŋko woni moƴƴo, jurmotooɗo tooɗo on"."
  52,29,"Anndintin tan, sabu neema Joomi maa oon, a wonaa ndureejo wonaa a kaangaaɗo."
  52,30,"Kaa ɓe mb'ay won'de : "Ko jimoowo ! Min habbitani mo tan jikke maayde"."
  52,31,"Maaku : "kabbitee ! Miin kadi miɗo habbitodi e mon"."